definitions.definition: A port town and borough in and the county town of Suffolk , England .
A city in southeastern Queensland , Australia .
A local government area around the city in Queensland ; in full, the City of Ipswich .
A coastal town and census-designated place therein, in Essex County , Massachusetts , United States .
A small city , the county seat of Edmunds County , South Dakota , United States .
An unincorporated community in the town of Elk Grove , Lafayette County , Wisconsin , United States .
